Class IndexOutput

    • ie.gmit.dip.IndexOutput
  • public class IndexOutput
extends java.lang.Object
    Since:
    1.8 The Output class is used for outputting indices with word definitions as a text to the console. It has also method to output indexed words (5 per line).
